mmj.gmff

Class MinDerivationStep

  • java.lang.Object
    • mmj.gmff.MinProofWorkStmt
      • mmj.gmff.MinProofStepStmt
        • mmj.gmff.MinDerivationStep

  • public class MinDerivationStep
extends MinProofStepStmt
    Derivation step on a MinProofWorksheet.

    Note: at this time GMFF does not need to know whether a proof step is an hypothesis or a derivation step, but MinHypothesisStep and MinDerivationStep are provided for completeness and future possibilities :-)

    • Constructor Detail

      • MinDerivationStep

        public MinDerivationStep(MinProofWorksheet w,
                         java.lang.String[][] slc)
        Standard MinDerivationStep constructor.
        Parameters:
        w - the MinProofworksheet object which contains the proof step.
        slc - Array of proof step lines each comprised of an Array of Strings called "chunks", which may be either Metamath whitespace or Metamath tokens. Hence the acronym "slc" refers to Statement Line Chunks.
